  {
    "name": "Welcome",
    "settings": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Theme settings allow you to customize the look and feel of your shop without having to delve into HTML or CSS code. Please see our [help page on theme settings](\/\/tm-lingerie-theme001.myshopify.com\/pages\/documentation) to learn more about how to customize your store."
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "In case of any issues with the theme feel free to contact our team at [shopify@template-help.com](mailto:shopify@template-help.com)"
